495
00:21:26,968 --> 00:21:28,234
i just want to thank you

496
00:21:28,302 --> 00:21:30,804
for, uh, getting me out of     
 that other deal so fast.

497
00:21:30,872 --> 00:21:33,390
Well, uh, let's say    
